<title>DAWTNAK NIH VAILAM AH A THLAI CH72</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vailam ah Khamhtu a thi, Thiannak cerhka a hun cang, Ka sualnak vialte
 a thianter lai, Dawtnak thukpi a ngeih ca, A Pa thutdan a kal tak, A kong
 zeihmanh ka chim kho rih lo.

[C1]
   Khenhmi thir nih an tlai lo, Siseh a ka dawtnak nih, Ka bawipa cu
   vailam ah a thlai, Ka caah thihnak a in, Kei cu mi luat ka si cang.
   (Jesuh lawng nih sual man a cham khawh).

[V2]
 Hnabei dong ka si lioah, Ka sual phawrh dingin a ra, Kei ca thi ding
 dang ho an um lo, Ka nunnak vialte ka pek, Thangthatnak hla ka sa lai,
 Khuaruahhar vel in a ka khamh ca.

[C2]
   Khenhmi thir nih an tlai lo, Siseh a ka dawtnak nih, Ka bawipa cu
   vailam ah a thlai, Ka caah thihnak a in, Kei cu mi luat ka si cang.
   (Jesuh lawng nih sual man a cham khawh).

[V3]
 Ka sual lung a thianter cang, Thlarau in a ka umpi Nifa ka thilrit a
 ka phawrhpiak. Ka vahvaihnak hmun kipah, Ka inn dawh cu ka naih chin, Cu
 hmun ah Bawipa cu ka hmuh lai.

[C3]
   Khenhmi thir nih an tlai lo, Siseh a ka dawtnak nih, Ka bawipa cu
   vailam ah a thlai, Ka caah thihnak a in, Kei cu mi luat ka si cang.
   (Jesuh lawng nih sual man a cham khawh).</lyrics>
</song>